---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Program">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">Program</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200">
      The detailed timetable will be refined over time. Explore the planned formats below and scroll down for the current event timeline.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a class="chip" href="#talks">Talks</a>
      <a class="chip" href="#posters">Posters</a>
      <a class="chip" href="#workshops">Workshops</a>
      <a class="chip" href="#panel">Panel</a>
      <a class="chip" href="#judging">Judging</a>
      <a class="chip" href="#networking">Networking</a>
      <a class="chip chip-active" href="#timeline">Timeline</a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div id="talks" class="card card-dark p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Team talks</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
          Short presentations by participating iGEM teams, including time for questions and technical transitions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div id="posters" class="card card-dark p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Poster session</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
          Present your project in an interactive poster format and receive direct feedback from peers and guests.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div id="workshops" class="card card-dark p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Workshops</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
          Hands-on sessions focused on useful iGEM-related skills and practical topics.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div id="panel" class="card card-dark p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Panel discussions</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
          Interactive discussions with invited guests on science, innovation, judging, and the broader iGEM experience.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div id="judging" class="card card-dark p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Judging session</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
          A dedicated judging and feedback format. Final details and criteria will be announced later.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div id="networking" class="card card-dark p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Networking</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
          Meet other teams, speakers, and guests in a relaxed setting throughout the event.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="timeline" class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 pb-16">
    <div class="card card-dark p-6 md:p-8">
      <div class="mb-8">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400">
          Event timeline
        </p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">Preliminary Schedule Overview</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-3xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
          This timeline gives a structured overview of the planned flow of the weekend. Times and individual sessions may still be adjusted.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <!-- Friday -->
        <details open class="group rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/80 p-5 shadow-sm dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900/50">
          <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4">
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400">
                Friday
              </p>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">July 10</h3>
            </div>
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 transition group-open:rotate-180 dark:text-slate-400">
              ▼
            </span>
          </summary>

          <div class="relative mt-6 pl-8">
            <div class="absolute left-[11px] top-0 h-full w-px bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700"></div>

            <div class="space-y-8">
              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute left-[-32px] top-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-xs text-slate-950 shadow-sm">
                  ⏱
                </div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">From 16:00</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Arrival & Check-in</p>
              </div>

              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute left-[-32px] top-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-xs text-slate-950 shadow-sm">
                  🎤
                </div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">17:00</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
                  Welcome Session, Opening Talk by Prof. Dr. Jochen Schmid
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute left-[-32px] top-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-xs text-slate-950 shadow-sm">
                  🌿
                </div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">18:00</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
                  Networking & Icebreaker Activities in the park, followed by dinner
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute left-[-32px] top-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-xs text-slate-950 shadow-sm">
                  🌃
                </div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">From 20:00 / 21:00</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
                  Explore Münster and continue the evening informally in the city
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Saturday -->
        <details open class="group rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/80 p-5 shadow-sm dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900/50">
          <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4">
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400">
                Saturday
              </p>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">July 11</h3>
            </div>
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 transition group-open:rotate-180 dark:text-slate-400">
              ▼
            </span>
          </summary>

          <div class="relative mt-6 pl-8">
            <div class="absolute left-[11px] top-0 h-full w-px bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700"></div>

            <div class="space-y-8">
              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute left-[-32px] top-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-xs text-slate-950 shadow-sm">☀️</div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">08:30</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Arrival</p>
              </div>

              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute left-[-32px] top-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-xs text-slate-950 shadow-sm">📋</div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">09:00</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
                  Welcome, overview of the day, and guest welcome
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute left-[-32px] top-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-xs text-slate-950 shadow-sm">🎙️</div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">09:45</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Speaker Session 1 </p>
              </div>

              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute left-[-32px] top-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-xs text-slate-950 shadow-sm">🎙️</div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">10:15</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Speaker Session 2 </p>
              </div>

              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute left-[-32px] top-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-xs text-slate-950 shadow-sm">💬</div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">10:45</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Judging Panel Discussion</p>
              </div>

              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute left-[-32px] top-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-xs text-slate-950 shadow-sm">☕</div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">11:15</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Coffee Break</p>
              </div>

              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute left-[-32px] top-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-xs text-slate-950 shadow-sm">🧪</div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">11:45</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Team Presentations — Block I</p>
              </div>

              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute left-[-32px] top-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-xs text-slate-950 shadow-sm">🍽️</div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">13:15</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Lunch Break</p>
              </div>

              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute left-[-32px] top-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-xs text-slate-950 shadow-sm">🧪</div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">14:00</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Team Presentations — Block II</p>
              </div>

              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute left-[-32px] top-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-xs text-slate-950 shadow-sm">☕</div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">15:30</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Coffee Break</p>
              </div>

              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute left-[-32px] top-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-xs text-slate-950 shadow-sm">🛠️</div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">15:45</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Workshops</p>
              </div>

              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute left-[-32px] top-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-xs text-slate-950 shadow-sm">🧾</div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">17:00</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Poster Session</p>
              </div>

              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute left-[-32px] top-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-xs text-slate-950 shadow-sm">🍽️</div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">18:00</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Closing & Dinner</p>
              </div>

              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute left-[-32px] top-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-xs text-slate-950 shadow-sm">🍻</div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">20:00</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Pub Quiz & Social Evening</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- Sunday -->
        <details open class="group rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white/80 p-5 shadow-sm dark:border-slate-800 dark:bg-slate-900/50">
          <summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-between gap-4">
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400">
                Sunday
              </p>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">July 12</h3>
            </div>
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 transition group-open:rotate-180 dark:text-slate-400">
              ▼
            </span>
          </summary>

          <div class="relative mt-6 pl-8">
            <div class="absolute left-[11px] top-0 h-full w-px bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700"></div>

            <div class="space-y-8">
              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute left-[-32px] top-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-xs text-slate-950 shadow-sm">🥐</div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">10:00</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Breakfast</p>
              </div>

              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute left-[-32px] top-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-xs text-slate-950 shadow-sm">🏆</div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">11:00</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">
                  Final Session: Judges’ Remarks, Awards Ceremony
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute left-[-32px] top-1 flex h-6 w-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-xs text-slate-950 shadow-sm">👋</div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white">From 12:30</p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Departure</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>